489
00:20:10,000 --> 00:20:13,041
What? Why am I in fifth place?

490
00:20:13,125 --> 00:20:15,166
I lost to Shiori.

491
00:20:15,250 --> 00:20:17,791
[AKANE] I'm not on the board,
but is that a good or bad thing?

492
00:20:17,875 --> 00:20:21,000
[NEWSCASTER B]
The third place sibling is.

493
00:20:21,083 --> 00:20:23,958
Princess Kanade!

494
00:20:24,041 --> 00:20:25,541
Uh. Sorry about that.

495
00:20:25,625 --> 00:20:26,791
Yeah, of course you are.

496
00:20:26,875 --> 00:20:28,583
[NEWSCASTER A]
Who will secure the top spot

497
00:20:28,666 --> 00:20:30,500
for this week's ranking?

498
00:20:30,583 --> 00:20:33,000
Will it be the first
princess, Aoi?

499
00:20:33,083 --> 00:20:36,375
Or the crime fighting
princess, Akane?

500
00:20:38,166 --> 00:20:41,083
[AKANE]
Oh, thank goodness!

501
00:20:41,166 --> 00:20:43,833
That's not good at all!

502
00:20:43,916 --> 00:20:45,875
I have to clean
bathrooms tomorrow.

503
00:20:45,958 --> 00:20:48,708
Everyone and their dog
saw my underwear.

504
00:20:48,791 --> 00:20:50,791
[crying]

505
00:20:50,875 --> 00:20:53,166
Akane, you've barely
touched your dinner.

506
00:20:53,250 --> 00:20:54,416
Is your tummy upset?

507
00:20:54,500 --> 00:20:55,333
[AKANE groans]

508
00:20:55,416 --> 00:20:56,666
[SHU sighs]

509
00:20:58,791 --> 00:21:00,625
[SOICHIRO] I know this has
been tough on you kids,

510
00:21:00,708 --> 00:21:03,125
but no one ever said that being
a member of the royal family

511
00:21:03,208 --> 00:21:04,666
was easy.

512
00:21:04,750 --> 00:21:07,375
Like it or not, you're going
to be scrutinized by the public.

513
00:21:07,458 --> 00:21:08,875
But you can't let it get to you.

514
00:21:08,958 --> 00:21:12,250
Being in the public eye is
simply one of your royal duties.

515
00:21:12,333 --> 00:21:15,166
You children are symbols
of hope for this country.

516
00:21:15,250 --> 00:21:17,625
Don't ever forget that.

517
00:21:17,708 --> 00:21:20,666
At this point, it's impossible
to guess who'll succeed me.

518
00:21:20,750 --> 00:21:22,958
But it's my duty to make
sure all of you are ready

519
00:21:23,041 --> 00:21:25,250
to take on that responsibility.

520
00:21:25,333 --> 00:21:27,083
That was a lovely speech, honey.

521
00:21:27,166 --> 00:21:30,125
But it's hard to take you
seriously with that thing on.

522
00:21:30,208 --> 00:21:33,291
I'll be sure to leave it
at the castle tomorrow.

523
00:21:36,333 --> 00:21:37,500
[AOI]
What're you doing, Akane?

524
00:21:37,583 --> 00:21:40,541
You should be sleeping.
Let's get to bed.

525
00:21:40,625 --> 00:21:43,916
[AKANE] I wish I could turn
into a blooming dandelion.

526
00:21:44,000 --> 00:21:45,000
[AOI]
Why?

527
00:21:45,083 --> 00:21:46,375
[AKANE]
I could ride the wind,

528
00:21:46,458 --> 00:21:49,541
away from people and
surveillance cameras.

529
00:21:50,958 --> 00:21:53,791
There is one way you
could fix your problems.

530
00:21:53,875 --> 00:21:56,625
All you have to do
is become king.

531
00:21:56,708 --> 00:21:59,250
That way you could abolish
the use of surveillance cameras,

532
00:21:59,333 --> 00:22:02,791
or even cancel the royal
family news altogether.

533
00:22:06,250 --> 00:22:08,750
[AKANE]
Aoi, I'm going to be king.

534
00:22:08,833 --> 00:22:10,125
[AOI]
Huh?

535
00:22:10,208 --> 00:22:13,291
Once I have the crown,
I'll live a quiet life.

536
00:22:13,375 --> 00:22:15,708
[AOI]
That sounds contradictory.

537
00:23:47,708 --> 00:23:49,583
[KANADE]
Hi, I'm Kanade Sakurada.

538
00:23:49,666 --> 00:23:51,333
[SATSUKI]
My sweet Kanade has always been

539
00:23:51,416 --> 00:23:52,791
an independent child.

540
00:23:52,875 --> 00:23:54,916
When she was younger
she loved to play royalty,

541
00:23:55,000 --> 00:23:57,375
and would run around
saying, "If you pwease,"

542
00:23:57,458 --> 00:23:59,208
just like a little princess.

543
00:23:59,291 --> 00:24:01,125
[KANADE] Thankfully those
days are behind me.

544
00:24:01,208 --> 00:24:02,583
[SATSUKI]
She may seem a little strict,

545
00:24:02,666 --> 00:24:05,625
but she's really a gentle
soul who loves her siblings.

546
00:24:05,708 --> 00:24:06,958
If she were to become king,

547
00:24:07,041 --> 00:24:09,166
the country would probably
be filled to the brim

548
00:24:09,250 --> 00:24:11,458
with hard-working,
orderly citizens.

549
00:24:11,541 --> 00:24:13,375
[KANADE]
Sounds like a Golden Age to me.

550
00:24:13,458 --> 00:24:16,000
Philip the II,
eat your heart out!

